steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi007f" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi007f" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicol007f" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi007f"
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I create new group API with name "groupapi007f"
Then I should see group api "groupapi007f" displayed in api list
When I select api name "groupapi007f" from list
When I add new API endpoint
When I set endpoint of API to value "/v1/jitera/delete/:id" in floating panel
When I set method of API to value "DELETE" in floating panel
When I set Name of Model to value "jitera delete" in floating panel
When I selec dropdown field "Model" of Model to value "jitapi007fs" in floating panel
When I selec dropdown field "Action" of Model to value "Delete" in floating panel
When I wait dropdown field "Action" is disabled in floating panel
When I add row Definition-Value with static value Table "2" - row "1" - value "jitapi007fs.jitapicol007f","static value","jitera delete"
